## Porting / legacy

Legacy reference lives in `api/src/*.js` (Express handlers + SQLite) and `web/src/` (Vite SPA). The modern path is `src/lib/clock/` + `src/app/api/`. When matching old behaviour, read the legacy file first, then implement in the domain layer вЂ” never edit the legacy trees.
